{
  "stem": "14168.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she, together with her younger sister, opened up one of the top millinery stores, fashion stores, in our city, even started before World War I.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that store I remember very well, because it was just destroyed by the Nazis a month before I left, in the course of the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They destroyed all the Jewish stores that they could get a hold of.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm hm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the town-- it was an interesting town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had a-- it had a long history, both as a city and also as far as the Jewish community was concerned.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had-- was about the size of San Francisco, 600,000 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A very vibrant Jewish community of 20,000.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- there was a-- we had three-- well, the city itself was on the Oder River.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it-- its origin goes back to the 10th-- I would say to 1000 approximately 1000.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was one of the focal points of-- of trade between the Baltic and the Adriatic Sea.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It also had a number of Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But, unfortunately, in 1453, they were driven out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came back in the 18th century, and they were--they settled there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had-- we had a great deal of Jewish thinkers, rabbis, who were leading both Orthodox, Conservative, and Liberal section, who were leading in the-- their respective movement.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One of them in particular was also a historian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was Heinrich Graetz, who wrote the And he taught at the seminary, where I later on studied.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But Breslau itself was a very important merch-- a commercial point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it had a university, a large university, which was also very well-known throughout the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It had a-- a great medical faculty, which was of note.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it-- it offered a very pleasant life.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
